In ver1.0,coudn't move as fast as we require for rhe system-took too much time for switching  movenent method and image processing method to follow the detected face correctly)

So,in ver 2.0,we adopt multi thread processing libraly "pthread" and succeed in improve the processing speed.

And more,we adopt Propotional control,and realized smoooth following.